Sika S.A. has recently signed up an agent in Namibia to represent their world-renowned construction materials in S.A.’s neighbouring country. Deon Koetze, owner of Shadow Marketing, based in Windhoek and his rep, Ian Snyman, have been instructed in the extensive product knowledge on the Sika range. Deon and Ian have also exhibited at the 2011 Windhoek Show, a considerable annual trade show, thereby creating greater awareness of the Sika brand and showcasing the products now available in Namibia.  During his visit to Windhoek, Sika S.A. Technical Sales Manager Phillip Boschoff also managed to give three intensive training sessions at Distributors, Pennypinchers Windhoek, Crown Build It and Pupkewitz Megabuild.